channel.title: Cursed - This Is Cursed (Album) (Electronic Rock)
channel.description:
Here's a Completely random album drop, full of re-released and unreleased tracks from Last year to a few months ago. Mainly B-sides, more Rock-centric music, Funk, Electronica, a remix of @OIL 's track "[**Times Of Need**](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9CmIL0ILdGQ)" and more!
[**Stream "This Is Cursed"**](https://soundcloud.com/cursed2/sets/this-is-cursed)
[![emilyalbum_Glitch|500x500](upload://a6YNOCBVLBFg9EE3b6SAP2Yl3pj.jpeg)](https://soundcloud.com/cursed2/sets/this-is-cursed)
Enjoy! :))
